data.description: One of the most desirable floor plans at St Germain Lofts! 3 large windows overlooking Main St. with Downtown views! The middle window opens, which is an upgraded option! High ceilings, exposed ductwork, & architectural elements create an urban loft experience. Reclaimed maple hardwood floors in LR/DR/Kitchen. Spacious bedroom features recent carpet (July 2020), & great closet organization system. Chefs Kitchen features dark stained cabinetry, granite tops & backsplash, SS appliances, and breakfast bar. Huge Bath has jetted tub/shower combo, dual sinks, & separate water closet! Nest thermostat, W/D in unit, 1 assigned garage parking space, & assigned storage closet in garage (only 14 units have these!). St Germain is located in the heart of Downtown near ALL Downtown attractions, & on MetroRail! A few blocks to Discovery Green Park, Market Sq Park, Theater District, Food Halls, Sporting Venues & more!
